{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel: message イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>name</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><em><code>message</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><code>message</code> イベントは、メッセージがそのチャネルに到着したときに <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a> オブジェクトに対して発生します。</span></p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>バブリング</td>\n   <td>なし</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">キャンセル</th>\n   <td>不可</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">インターフェイス</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">イベントハンドラプロパティ</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\" title=\"onmessage\"><code>onmessage</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"live_example","title":"実例","isH3":true,"content":"<p>この例では、ユーザーがボタンをクリックしたときに <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a> の内容を放送する \"Sender\" の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a> と、放送メッセージを受信し、その結果を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> 要素に書き込む2つの \"Receiver\" の <code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code> があります。</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"sender\" name=\"Sender\">Sender</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> channel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'example-channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> messageControl <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> broadcastMessageButton <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#broadcast-message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nbroadcastMessageButton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    channel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>messageControl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"receiver_1\" name=\"Receiver_1\">Receiver 1</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> channel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'example-channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nchannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  received<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"receiver_2\" name=\"Receiver_2\">Receiver 2</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> channel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'example-channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nchannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  received<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"結果","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"dummy\" title=\"Sender sample\" id=\"frame_sender\" width=\"100%\" height=\"170px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/_sample_.sender.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"dummy\" title=\"Receiver 1 sample\" id=\"frame_receiver_1\" width=\"100%\" height=\"150px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/_sample_.receiver_1.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"dummy\" title=\"Receiver 2 sample\" id=\"frame_receiver_2\" width=\"100%\" height=\"150px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/_sample_.receiver_2.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-message\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML Living Standardの仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.message_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>関連イベント: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\" title=\"messageerror\"><code>messageerror</code></a>。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"message イベントは、メッセージがそのチャネルに到着したときに BroadcastChannel オブジェクトに対して発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BroadcastChannel: message event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"message","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"BroadcastChannel: message event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event/